job.description:
Requirements for candidates:
technology or engineering experience in production;
physics or mechanics education;
technician talent and salesman's enthusiasm;
good project management skills;
ability to learn technical information;
good Estonian, English knowledge;
excellent negotiation and negotiation skills;
experience in active sales (desirable);
independence in work planning, ability to cooperate with a team;
a category B driver's license is required.

Job description:
direct work (representing exclusive and innovative products) with industrial companies in all Estonia;
analysis of customer needs technical engineering consultations, preparation of commercial offers and organization o  the sales process;
engineering consultations, preparation of commercial offers and organization of the sales process;
cooperation with our suppliers research and product development departments in finding ways to solve customer problems;
all necessary technical support and training from colleagues working in the company and training organized by suppliers,
you will go to presentations/trainings at various international exhibitions;
prospect of building your own team;
a working culture that constantly encourages personal and professional growth
a modern work environment, great colleagues, and the freedom to create and work independently
a motivational system focused on achieving results.

What we offer:
direct sales, representing exclusive, innovative products, for manufacturing companies in Estonia, analysis of customer needs and preparation of offers;
organization of project sales and implementation;
approaching new customers, maintaining relationships with existing ones; cooperation with suppliers in solving customer needs;
training in the company and supplier courses, visiting various exhibitions;
working environment for personal and professional growth;
modern working environment and creative freedom;
results-oriented bonus system;
company car, telephone and computer.
